                     That the Romane is the One, Holy, Catholike, Apostolical Church, from, &amp; by which we are to receyue the Tradition of Christian Doctrine. §. 5.
                     THIS Ground being laid, it is apparent that the Romane Church, that is the multitude of Christians spread ouer the world, cleauing to the doctrine and Tradition of the Church of Rome, is the only holy, Catholike, and Apostolicall Church.
                     
